<p><strong><em>Innate Spellcasting.</em></strong> The barlguraâ€™s spellcasting ability is Wisdom (spell save DC 13). The barlgura can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components:</p>

<p>1/day each: entangle, phantasmal force</p>

